{"data": [{"id": "4747443", "title": "Time In The Market Beats Timing The Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Timing The Market\" data-id=\"171242305\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"3872px\" height=\"2592px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">A_Carina</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>It was another great year in the stock market. But predicting the timing of a bear or bull market is more challenging. Fortunately for investors, the stock market is up a lot more of the time than it is down. More specifically, over the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/171242305/image_171242305.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747443-time-in-market-beats-timing-the-market", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 12:25:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747433", "title": "American Airlines Is Poised To Continue Its Ascent", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"American Airlines A319 taking off at Charlotte Douglas International Airport\" data-id=\"537126290\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\">American Airlines operates its second largest hub at Charlotte Douglas International Airport</p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Laser1987</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Several U.S. airline industry stocks had an impressive run in 2025, particularly among the legacy carriers, or those that served interstate routes at the time the domestic airline industry</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/537126290/image_537126290.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747433-american-airlines-is-poised-to-continue-its-ascent", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 12:05:31", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747439", "title": "Palantir And Duolingo: The AI Powerhouses Driving AGIX's Success", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"AI logo place on abstract blocks\" data-id=\"1795495467\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">J Studios</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>The <a href=\"https://kraneshares.com/agix\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">KraneShares Artificial Intelligence and Technology ETF</a> (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/AGIX\" title=\"KraneShares Artificial Intelligence ETF\">AGIX</a>) has demonstrated impressive performance since its inception on July 18, 2024, with a total return of 13.48%.<sup>1</sup> This outpaces other significant market benchmarks and AI-themed indexes.</p> <p>KraneShares also hosted a</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1795495467/image_1795495467.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747439-palantir-duolingo-ai-powerhouses-driving-agix-success", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:55:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747429", "title": "Yum! Brands: Taco Bell Eyes Dutch Bros' Success", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Young Asian man driving a car\" data-id=\"2189792154\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">ISMOLOEX/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>One Swallow Does Not Make a Summer</h2> <p><a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4736292-yum-brands-the-golden-rosemary-is-still-taco-bell-other-brands-still-under-pressure\">Yum! Brands</a> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/YUM\" title=\"Yum! Brands, Inc.\">YUM</a></span>) is experiencing the \u2018Fast-Food Exodus\u2019 in an uneven fashion, as evidenced by the recent performance of its brand portfolio. While KFC, Pizza Hut and Habit Burger are struggling</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2189792154/image_2189792154.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747429-yum-brands-taco-bell-eyes-dutch-bros-success", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:32:03", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747428", "title": "Moderna: From Breakthrough COVID-19 Vaccines To Personalized Cancer Therapies", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Gloved Hand Holding Cancer Vaccine with Syringe on Orange Background\" data-id=\"1284796611\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Cindy Shebley/iStock via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Moderna's origins and business overview</h2> <p>Moderna, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/MRNA\" title=\"Moderna, Inc.\">MRNA</a></span>), is a biotechnology company focused on developing and commercialising messenger-RNA ((mRNA)) based therapies, targeting a diversity of therapeutic areas including prophylactic vaccines against respiratory infections, personalised cancer therapies, and rare diseases. Moderna</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1284796611/image_1284796611.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747428-moderna-stock-from-breakthrough-covid-19-vaccines-to-personalised-cancer-therapies-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:29:16", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747432", "title": "EPR Properties: The Big Dividend Yield Is A Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Topgolf: Golf, Party Venue, Sports Bar &amp; Restaurant, Germantown, MD\" data-id=\"1414473405\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Tim Pruss/iStock Editorial via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>REITs have been melting over the last few months in direct response to a surge in long-term yields. The US 10-year Treasury yield is approaching more than half a decade high, driving up the risk-free</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1414473405/image_1414473405.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747432-epr-properties-big-dividend-yield-is-a-buy", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:15:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747425", "title": "Equinox Gold: Higher Production, But Waning Per Share Metrics", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Pouring liquid gold into graphite casting form from furnace\" data-id=\"1395487823\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1022px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Nordroden</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><em>All figures are in United States Dollars unless otherwise noted. G/T = grams per tonne (of gold or silver). GEOs = gold-equivalent ounces. SEOs = silver-equivalent ounces. AISC refers to all-in sustaining costs. LOMP = life of mine plan. TPD = tonnes per day.</em></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1395487823/image_1395487823.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747425-equinox-gold-higher-production-waning-per-share-metrics", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:08:20", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747431", "title": "Monetary Policy Trumps Tariffs", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Torn bills revealing Monetary Policy words\" data-id=\"1298888376\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5184px\" height=\"3456px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Tast Nawarat</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>There's no need to worry about Trump's threatened tariffs causing another bout of inflation. Inflation is a monetary phenomenon that can only be caused by excess money, not artificially jacked-up prices. A sound monetary policy deals with rising prices for some</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1298888376/image_1298888376.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4747431-monetary-policy-trumps-tariffs", "pub_date": "2025-01-03 11:00:00", "source": "seekalpha_articles", "kind": 1, "language": "en"}, {"id": "4747421", "title": "VFVA: Limited Growth Potential In An AI-Driven Market", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Values Word Cloud\" data-id=\"2170991268\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"931px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2170991268/image_2170991268.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024